# Mastermind member count

In the “Join the HTSA Mastermind Community” step, use **over 470 members** (not 440+ or other numbers unless CJ updates this rule).

Example sentence:  
`Request access to the private Facebook Mastermind — where all live coaching call replays are posted and over 470 members support each other 24/7.`
